media:group.media:title: DevFest Europe Keynote 2022
media:group.media:description:
We are excited to welcome people in-person and online for DevFest 2022! Hear about the impactful projects people are working on at various GDG chapters in Europe. Learn about the technologies and motives behind these projects with plans to help restore environmental degradation, create clean energy from hydrogen, and more! Discover how developers use Google technologies to create innovative solutions together. 

Learn more about Google Developer Groups → https://goo.gle/3laRM8p 
Find a Google Developer Group hosting a DevFest near you → https://goo.gle/3Tty2fX 
Follow our European ​Twitter channel to hear more from our communities, programs, and events!  →  https://goo.gle/GoogleDevEurope-Twitter 

Chapters:
0:00 - Show opener
0:29 - Welcome from Florina Muntenescu, Android Developer Relations Engineer at Google
3:24 - Community Highlights with Alessandro Palmieri, Google Developers Groups Program Lead in Europe
3:58 - GDG Lleida, Dronecoria
4:17 - GDG Athens
4:35 - GDG Burgos
4:59 - GDG Lisbon
5:15 - Solution Challenge projects from Europe
6:00 - Hearts with Ukraine 
6:57 -  Closing remarks

Speakers:
Florina Muntenescu - Android Developer Relations Engineer at Google
Alessandro Palmieri - Google Developers Groups Program Lead in Europe
